{"tid":105333,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"合味道喇沙味真係好撚高汁","createTime":"2017-02-02T19:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T09:22:17.000Z","uid":638,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d320c9e2011b0a7c330391f9452d279ac39b22b3","tid":105333,"uid":638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T19:52:16.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽3點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餓餓地緊係食個杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完打3隻蛋落去 攞去叮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ot3E4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ot3E4J.jpg&h=a02c64d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叮完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/034349_da8206946eb431607b3b54f364373ba5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F034349_da8206946eb431607b3b54f364373ba5.jpg&h=76bd9871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太多所以倒咗啲落隻碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5K49A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5K49A4.jpg&h=13148fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一放入口發現真係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玻璃碗就叮得比較老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然個表面老老地 但係中間正到痴線 入口勁滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經食用完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfaff81bd57709847e18ac602e683bd91ea55af","tid":105333,"uid":638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0